posts.post_content:
Posted By: John Wondowski
Breaking a set of T200 Fatima Team Cards.  The set was put together with cards with excellent contrast which is often lacking in this issue.  All cards are SGC graded and priced includes delivery - quantity discounts are available, but first email that says "I'll take it!" gets it.  Please email to reserve or for questions.  I take checks or paypal.  Thank you.

John (jwondowski@aol.com)
